This webhook fires when an order message is created by customer or in control panel.

### Example callback:

```json
{
  "created_at": 1561482670,
  "store_id": "1025646",
  "producer": "stores/{store_hash}",
  "scope": "store/order/message/created",
  "hash": "352e4afc6dd3fc85ea26bfdf3f91852604d57528",
 "data": {
    "type": "order",
    "id": 250,
    "message": {
      "order_message_id": 3
    }
  }
}
```

